{"tid":1763203,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我覺得我地應該要設死線","createTime":"2019-11-30T07:00:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T07:47:47.000Z","uid":153981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"63be2ec705e6f2310990197fe0a59b89b3329ee9","tid":1763203,"uid":153981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T07:00:40.000Z","msg":"雖然只係p牌仔，但都想講d野。其實區選大勝同埋侵侵簽法案助攻，再加上全球都要圍堵支那（澳洲間諜案、日本荷蘭加拿大英國都想整人權法案），比左個好好嘅勢比香港。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家政府係我地大勝後繼續冷處理五大訴求，其實原則上係佢地有問題。我地應該要設條死線，如果政府再唔做野，我地應該要重新開始新一輪攻勢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n區選到依家已經成個星期，比曬時間佢地回應，佢地選擇只係放風整個獨立「檢討」委員會，一d野都沒做過。我地應該吹大雞重新集結，要重新集結我地力量，迎頭痛擊支那共產黨！設死線！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc61eb4704c004c3dd45ce4d0744370d779b3d60","tid":1763203,"uid":267052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T07:47:47.000Z","msg":"12.9三罷算唔算又一條死線<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\"